Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:15.24,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible to have a happy\N marriage to a human woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:18.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:26.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And this time, I'll prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:30.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll prove it with our eternal love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:06.93,sign_2925_6_Hoozuki_City_s_4,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hozuki City's 48th  \N 7/24-25 Kagurazaka Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:06.89,Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,550)}#6 "Devil and Sense of Loss"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:12.44,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}July 15th\N  Shinjuku Ward Kagurazaka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.26,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi, are you over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.44,Default - Top,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:17.46,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Six wins in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long, I've lost my intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.49,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak now that you're\N a productive member of society, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.60,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Super weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having me over tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Helping with the family\Nbusiness again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:41.84,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We got a lot of reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's rough when your parents\N own a restaurant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.59,Default,gi,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is rough when your\N parents own a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:49.48,Default,gi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.73,Default,gi,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go to Kagurazaka\N Festival with me next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.89,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Kagurazaka Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you be helping your family then, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to get them to give me time off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:02.24,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's on a weekday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:05.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can go before work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You're paying, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.62,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.36,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding! That was a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:14.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I've\N been to a festival with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.81,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:18.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:40.78,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.78,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I finally lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.67,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That guard dog of yours is persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.08,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.78,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:56.54,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So this is her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.80,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Which parts of the earlier girl were right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.36,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Voice and right leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The eye, which goes in last, is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.22,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is the left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:14.91,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I found a girl who I think\N will meet your conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:18.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.76,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,As near as I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.45,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's for your help earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:29.08,sign_6341_55_Storage__1,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Storage #1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.33,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Morn—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.56,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.58,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.49,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.21,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Senda-san, are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.18,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.82,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a work trip to Romania\N for the next two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:45.97,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Romania?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:48.21,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You're going overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.80,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.64,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I would be, if it weren't for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.98,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys hold down the fort\N for the next two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:56.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:00.54,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:01.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Head out on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:02.86,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.74,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what happened at Toyama Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:08.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.27,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,One of the female victims woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.25,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.75,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So you need to go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.94,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoichi's on the way there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.63,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:23.32,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I've got analysis work to do. You two handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.82,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Visiting hours are almost over, so hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.89,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:31.39,sign_7850_82_July_16th,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}July 16th
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.30,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.74,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the information from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.09,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Shiba Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She's fully conscious\N and remembers everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:51.72,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,so we were able to find out her\N address and her family information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The issue is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.50,sign_8266_90_Birthdate__11_10,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Birthdate: 11/10/1965
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.75,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Born in 1965?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.18,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If this is true, she's in her 50s.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.98,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But she doesn't look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to think she's a teenager, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:10.06,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, does that mean she was \Na teenager when she was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:12.78,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and then she came back without aging?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:13.90,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.80,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Typical of a supernatural disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiba Yuko-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.49,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakaki Kyoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:33.53,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Shinjuku Ward Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.21,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.03,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:53.18,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't remember much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.02,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.72,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling? Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.81,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:11.05,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,First, can you tell me what school you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a second year student\N at Shirakoma Girls Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.88,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my childhood friend goes there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard they have a good choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They go to national tournaments all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.24,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.59,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I joined to be part of the choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:33.96,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We were all looking forward\N to going to nationals this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.60,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.60,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.40,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.51,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,After practice ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:50.18,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Everything just went black,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.40,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and it was dark for so long after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Was there light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:56.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:02.70,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But I could see my hands and stuff, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:08.49,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And blackness... it was like ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:11.13,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Or fine sand. Falling from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Black sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.19,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:27.26,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... my throat\Nwould sometimes feel cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.78,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Like someone put a knife to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:37.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No... but when I remembered,\N I suddenly got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice sounds normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little husky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.54,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Husky? Nobody's ever said that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you try singing a high note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Like you did in choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.53,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.90,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:03.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.13,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.74,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So, she lost function in\N a specific body part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the natural assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In her case, she's retained\N her ability to speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,but lost function in a certain vocal range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.00,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Her singing voice was stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.90,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.58,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:30.58,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a call. Another victim woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.70,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But they say her right leg won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.46,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't get hurt or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.55,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking into it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.61,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,but there's another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.71,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Another problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.98,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She went missing in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.48,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we need to look into this more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.75,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And work with the police, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Work with the police, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:58.88,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The cops and ward office have\N different things they can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.36,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,First, head back here. I want\N to show you what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.16,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only possibility, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:36.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:43.70,sign_7850_82_July_16th,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}July 18th
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,First, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.27,sign_16014_175_Unsolved_Missing,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Unsolved Missing Girls Cases in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The part with a red bookmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is the girl from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:19.78,sign_16167_177_Name__Shiba_Yuko,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Name:{\b1} Shiba Yuko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:19.52,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There's a missing persons case\N I've been following for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:23.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I think these girls are its victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This many?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:28.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look at the blue bookmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki-san, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.23,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.67,sign_16656_185_Name__Sakaki_Shi,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Name:{\b1} Sakaki Shiori{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She's my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:42.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,17 years ago, we lost our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us lived in an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:48.99,Flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.56,Flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.81,Flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You had me so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.41,Flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.71,Flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.68,Flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't get violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:03.82,Flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If you hit first, it becomes your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:08.34,Flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home. The nuns are worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:12.64,Flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.18,Flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.95,Flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee... chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:48.38,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She was kidnapped by an\N Another right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:53.16,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I had no idea\N it was an Another, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.17,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:59.98,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, I've been searching\N for the one who kidnapped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:03.45,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Searching? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:11.04,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But all I learned from that is that the police\N can't help you with Another-related cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:17.69,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,After that, a lot happened. I became\N a host because I needed the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.69,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's when Senda-san found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:26.29,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when I realized that at this\N Nocturnal Community Relations job,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.47,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to find a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:33.08,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And I suppose I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.61,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.03,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The black sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.84,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What she talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.37,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.25,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I think that the one who kidnapped\N the girls we found in Toyama Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:45.95,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,and the one who kidnapped my sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.59,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,are either the same Another,\N or the same type of Another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.40,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Huehuecóyotl said?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:56.69,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That there was a nasty devil\N that went around collecting girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.76,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:04.61,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you act as a go-between\N and let me talk to Huehuecóyotl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:17.79,Flashback_Italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The man you were with held a tremendous \Nsense of loss, and that tripped the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.63,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.54,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki-san's sense of loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,When you say "talk," do you mean "negotiate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:30.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You said that human common sense\N doesn't work on Anothers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're right to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to negotiate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.08,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't negotiate. I just want\N to hear what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.88,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sakaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:55.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to Kohaku when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.21,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you one, Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.92,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Also, this is absolutely not work-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So don't tell Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:14.22,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Senda-san's not here, so I don't\N want to cause extra problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,When it's time, I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:20.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.40,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.39,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.49,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She might be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:39.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking...\N that your sister might be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.40,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The girl in the hospital was born in 1965.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And she came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think she might be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.38,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:00.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.15,sign_23177_259_March_Chiyoda_An,Top,0000,0000,0000,,March{\b0\fs18} Chiyoda Another Accident Reports
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.15,sign_23177_260_August_Shinjuku_,Side,0000,0000,0000,,August{\b0\fs18} Shinjuku Another\N Accident Reports
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.54,sign_7850_82_July_16th,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,July 23rd
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.29,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:30.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You missed another thing\N on your paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.58,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've been screwing up\N all the time since last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've been kind of weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.29,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Want to get some fresh air, Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take him on patrol?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess it's that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In this state, he's just\N getting in the way, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:00.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:01.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are hiding something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:11.33,sign_24644_278_Umeya,,0000,0000,0000,,Umeya
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see Kohaku yesterday, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:17.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've waited 17 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:28.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think we should tell Theo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.68,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This whole thing is just me being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for getting you involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to keep that at a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.76,sign_25841_291_Hoozuki_City_s_4,,0000,0000,0000,,Hozuki City's 48th Awa Dance \N 7/24-25 Kagurazaka Festival 7/26-27
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:01.76,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}July 24th
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.25,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:12.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We just sounded like we\N were from some old manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd actually say that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:16.85,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.09,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it does feel a little unlike us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.08,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have time before work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:26.51,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave at 6:30, I'll make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:27.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.71,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:46.00,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Something that's not carbonated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.06,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:05.70,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.49,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.09,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's finally showing up late for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:21.25,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It happens to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:23.07,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been any incident reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.60,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.06,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.08,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.06,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.10,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.66,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can't tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.67,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,How long have we known each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.20,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:42.50,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of my business what\N you do when you're off the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.07,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But think about the new kid a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.83,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's interfering with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.22,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.21,sign_28561_326_Miyako_Arata__Sh,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako Arata\N {\fs18}Shinjuku Ward Nocturnal Community Relations
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.21,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.53,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.58,Italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They took her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.35,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:02.96,sign_28726_331_Miyako_Arata__Sh,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako Arata\N {\fs18}Shinjuku Ward Nocturnal Community Relations
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:03.80,Italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi... my childhood friend... was taken \Nby an Another right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.36,Italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the one you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:09.58,Italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The one who took your sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.58,Italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,They were surrounded by black sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Black sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.52,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Like we saw in Toyama Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:20.11,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's got nothing to do with your sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.99,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Or does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.33,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Kyoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,During the Toyama Park incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.01,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,it occurred to me that Huehuecóyotl\N might have information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:38.04,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried to talk to him, using Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.09,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,"Talk to him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.20,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiating with them is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:48.72,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You lectured the rookie,\N and then you go and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay put. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.73,sign_30132_349_Miyako_Arata__Sh,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako Arata\N {\fs18}Shinjuku Ward Nocturnal Community Relations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:58.98,Italics,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.34,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.59,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What are the odds...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.36,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.62,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Kohaku, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.20,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You're here, right? Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:18.00,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You called?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:52.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I like that look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.68,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I never really got to see it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:56.93,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:59.73,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:01.94,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one you should be mad at.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:07.51,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's that devil who's collecting\N all the human females.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:11.11,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The ones I used in the\N kyoshi ritual, and now her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:13.70,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me! Where is Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:19.21,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,A place you cannot reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:21.27,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:22.46,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:29.92,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Hell.
